      "content": "interesting. so u think it was a sort of perfect synergy? cuz i've read some stuff that says the more radical groups were actually seen as a threat to the whole progress being made, or even that the government used the threat of them to make MLK look more \"reasonable\" by comparison. do u think it was actually a \"convergence\" like u said, or was it more about one side basically being used to push the other through?",
